show all stopwords categories of a language

Source: R/stopwords.R
show_sw.Rd

show all stopwords categories of a language

show_sw(lang, as_vector = FALSE)

Arguments

lang

language, like "en", "pt"

Value

an list object of stopwords

Examples

show_sw("pt")
